Financial Gravity Tax Announces New Partner Office in Cumming, Georgia



                                            07/25/2017 by Financial Gravity 
                                        

 Allen, TX – (NASDAQ Wire – July 25, 2017) Financial Gravity Tax, Inc. a subsidiary of Financial Gravity Companies, Inc (OTCQB: FGCO) is proud to partner with Mark Miller and Exclusive Business Solutions located in Cumming, Georgia. Exclusive Business Solutions offers consulting services to allow their clients to implement financial solutions.
Exclusive Business Solutions, Inc. (a partner company with Safe Money Strategies) consults with business owners, top executives, physicians, and high net worth individuals to help them protect their financial assets and live the life they deserve. They help business owners take their company to the next level by providing thoughtful and innovative financial planning by identifying strategies and tactical solutions to preserve, promote and protect the value of clients’ businesses and assets.
“I am proud to be partnered with Financial Gravity. My company, Exclusive Business Solutions, has long been looking for a firm that can give my business clients outstanding ways to lessen their tax burdens and expand their company profits. I think Financial Gravity has the strategies, personnel and expertise to serve my clients well, both now and in the future. We’re extremely excited about our new partnership!,” expressed Mark Miller, Owner of Exclusive Business Solutions.
Dave Crowley, Financial Gravity President and Chief Strategy Officer, stated, “We’re excited to add our first Advisor Partner from the state of Georgia. Mark has built a successful company that is already focused on supporting the small business community. We both get to expand our footprint in this active market and really help Small Business Owners stop wasting and overpaying their tax bills.”
About Financial Gravity Companies, Inc. 
Financial Gravity Companies, Inc., a Fractional Family Office ®, provides integrated tax, business, and financial solutions. Clients include small business owners and high net-worth individuals. Services are focused on helping its clients’ personal and professional goals, while building wealth, most often with potential tax savings, lowering costs, and improving efficiency. For details, visit www.financialgravity.com.
