Tax Planning, Coaching & Preparation Services Dallas | Financial Gravity

































  
 






















Call 469-342-9100			




















Lowering taxes increases profitability and grows wealth. Unlike other tax-related services and solutions, at Financial Gravity we’re committed to working with you personally to proactively develop a plan to minimize your tax burden and maximize your success.
 







It’s not rocket science. It’s simple math.
Our tax offerings include:










Tax Blueprint® After a simple 15-30 minute no obligation assessment, we’ll determine if we can substantially reduce your tax burden. If so, we will develop a tax savings plan utilizing our exclusive Tax Blueprint®. The Tax Blueprint® provides a clear tax reduction plan that is customized specifically to you and your business.
Sources of tax savings, along with implementation plans, are highlighted and summarized so you can be confident that the savings are real. You can expect that the total reduction of your taxes will be substantially higher than the cost of the service itself.  This is backed up by our 2X savings guarantee. That means you’ll never pay more than half of what we save you in tax savings. It doesn’t get easier than that.





Fractional Family Office™ Take the financial performance of your company to the next level.  Get all the benefits of a seasoned CFO/COO to help guide financial decision-making at a fraction of the cost of a full-time executive resource.
This solution includes:

A professional resource dedicated to your team
Strategic financial modeling, reports, and analysis of your business using the latest computer-based tools and methods
Common sense recommendations on how to improve financial performance of your company
Monthly meetings to review the latest reports, analysis, and recommendations to maximize financial performance
Access to a trusted financial expert who understands you and your business

This offering is designed to work as a standalone solution or in direct coordination with the Tax Operating System® and related Bookkeeping with Purpose®; solutions. In addition, it requires a 12-month subscription that can be cancelled anytime with a 60-day notice.





Exit Planning Selling a business is both exciting and stressful.  If the transaction isn’t structured appropriately it can also be one of the biggest tax events of your lifetime.  With exit planning assistance from Financial Gravity we can help advise and instruct you on how to avoid costly mistakes so you can keep more of what you earn.
Our solution includes:

A confidential one-on-one assessment with one of our tax planning specialists to understand the details of the sale.
A customized set of practical recommended tax reduction strategies that are designed to meet the needs of your situation.
Assistance implementing the strategies so you can ensure you’re not unnecessarily “leaving money on the table.”

This offering is designed to work in direct coordination with the Tax Operating System® and related Bookkeeping with Purpose®; solutions.  We offer exit planning as a free service for all Financial Gravity clients who are enrolled in both a tax and wealth solution.
If you are not a Financial Gravity client, or only enrolled in one of our solutions, then we charge a consulting fee for this offering.





Tax Operating System® With the Tax Operating System® you can choose the level that works best for you. Designed to fit any budget and circumstance, our exclusive suite of solutions enable implementation of the Tax Blueprint® to help you save money.
Regardless of which solution you select, you can count on access to our advisors, annual tax planning assistance, ongoing newsletter, and educational materials.
Solutions include:
Advisory
You are provided with direct access to our certified tax advisors to review questions, scenarios, and changes to your business and personal life as it relates to the plan. Our Certified Tax Masters® will provide you with the guidance, recommendations, and support to ensure your tax savings are maximized. This service is $95 per month and can be cancelled at any time.
Additionally, the advisory solution includes optional setup of IRS support documentation and business structure filings to enable you to implement your Tax Blueprint® with confidence. This requires a one-time $995 fee.
Advisory & Tax Preparation
In addition to the advisory solution, we also offer our clients timely tax preparation services, IRS representation and IRS audit protection. We also manage setup of all IRS support documentation and business structure filings. Based on the complexity of your business, this service is offered at $200 – $350 per month and the $995 setup fee is waived.
Bookkeeping with Purpose®
Beyond the benefits of the advisory and tax preparation solutions, we also help you implement all recommended tax strategies with our complete bookkeeping and payroll services. Our proprietary Bookkeeping with Purpose® methodology ensures you are achieving the tax savings from your Tax Blueprint® and that every expense is appropriately accounted for in relation to your Tax Blueprint®.
We work closely with you to keep your books current and accurate. We are proactively engaged in your business, continually focused on your goals of cost savings, wealth building, increasing profit and retirement savings, and presenting other unique profit opportunities.
This solution also includes powerful and actionable business intelligence reports that highlight performance insights on your operation and finances.
Not only does Bookkeeping with Purpose® reduce the headache of having to manage your books and payroll – it also provides you with the confidence that everything is being managed appropriately to reduce your tax burden. This service is offered starting at $395 per month and may increase based on the size and complexity of your business.





Advanced Tax Operating System™ Our Advanced Tax Operating System™ includes all of the benefits and services of our Tax Operating System®, but is designed to help higher earning business owners, as well as W2 employees consistently earning over $300,000 per year. This offering creates an amazing holistic strategy and system to ensure maximum tax savings and benefits for the client’s family and dependents.
Our solution includes:

The Tax Operating System® benefits
Personal Family Office Strategy™
Private Indemnification Strategy™
Employee Stock Ownership Trust
Private Family Legacy Endowment™
Personal Family Bank™
Zero Estate Tax Strategy™
...and MUCH more!









 













 







Wealth & Investment Planning Dallas | Financial Gravity

































  
 






















Call 469-342-9100			




















Unlike traditional brokerages that make money from each transaction, or companies that typically sell a limited set of financial products, we are an independent financial advisory firm. That means we can address your wealth management needs holistically by developing strategies that address all aspects of your investments. Plus, we use the latest analytic tools, portfolio management platforms, and the most diverse set of financial investment vehicles available. It’s a unique approach that’s centered on your success.
 







We believe financial planning, wealth management, and risk management should work hand-in-hand.










Wealth Blueprint™ Using PortfolioGPS™, our most advanced financial planning system, one of our trusted financial advisors will sit down with you in person to review your specific needs, goals, and preferences. 
We will design a customized investment recommendation based on your unique needs. Additionally, this plan will include proven tax-reduction strategies that are designed to maximize your wealth.





Wealth Operating System™ Offered in three tiers, the Wealth Operating System™ is designed to implement your financial plan. Tier 2 and 3 include the Wealth Blueprint™, and Tier 1 includes our more basic Foundations Plan. In addition to the Wealth Blueprint, each tier includes a long list of benefits and services designed to get you from where you are to where you want to be. Face it, most plans go unimplemented, and that’s why the Wealth Operating System is designed and priced to put implementation within your reach. A plan is only a roadmap. Implementation puts you in the car and on the road to attaining your goals, with us as your trusted navigator and advisor, and portfolio access and insights are available 24/7 via one of the most sophisticated, reliable, and user friendly technology platforms in the industry.
To further differentiate ourselves from traditional brokerage firms, our fee structure is completely transparent. There are no hidden fees or daily calls from some sales broker trying to get you to buy or sell a financial product so “they” can earn a commission.
Plain and simple – with Financial Gravity, we offer solid wealth management that you can count on.
This solution includes:

Wealth Blueprint (PortfolioGPS Advanced Financial Plan or Foundations Basic Plan)
Annual and quarterly face-to-face meetings to review progress and performance
On-Demand Advice (phone/email)
Free Notary Service
Culture Index - Professional Personality Profile
Tax Return $149 or free if AUM greater than $500,000
Activation and setup of all Wealth Management online platforms and portals for you to access your investment performance at any-time 
Charitable Tax Strategies
Special Needs Planning
Management of all paperwork and signatures to execute the plan 
Regular education sessions including webinars, live events, newsletters, and other publications 






Estate Planning You’ve worked hard over an entire lifetime to generate meaningful wealth.  You deserve the peace of mind that comes from knowing that every possible action has been taken to decrease taxes and increase what gets passed on for future generations.
Our estate planning solution is designed to work in coordination with our other tax and wealth solutions to maximize the overall impact to your bottom line.
Our estate planning solution includes:

One on one consultation with a certified wealth strategist and guidance from one of our Certified Tax Masters
A confidential conversation regarding your needs and priorities
A complete and easy to understand review of various options related to tax minimization strategies, trusts, wills, charities, beneficiaries, business continuity, gifts, insurance, and other concerns
Help structuring and implementing a holistic estate plan
Introduction to trusted partners for legal assistance
Direct and active integration with your broader wealth and tax management strategies

While this solution is primarily designed to assist our active tax, wealth, and business solution clients, we are also glad to offer this service broadly based on a standard financial advisory fee.





Risk Management Minimizing risk is a critical part of any well-crafted financial plan.  Because we are an independent financial advisory firm we can objectively help you manage the complexity of the insurance industry to ensure you get the maximum amount of benefits at the best price.
Our offering includes:

A personalized risk assessment that takes into account your lifestyle, personal needs, and broader wealth strategy
A custom analysis of the best products in the overall marketplace that meets your personal criteria
Our experienced staff will provide assistance reviewing and negotiating plans from different providers to ensure you get the most benefits at the lowest cost
